driving rural economic development.

152
00:10:33,512 --> 00:10:36,433
However,
alongside the rapid growth of TVEs,

153
00:10:36,992 --> 00:10:39,193
corruption has gradually surfaced,

154
00:10:39,592 --> 00:10:41,232
becoming a focus of societal concern.

155
00:10:45,592 --> 00:10:48,913
A certain leader in Yuehai has always
been strong-willed and decisive.

156
00:10:49,352 --> 00:10:52,232
At the city's founding,
he pushed through opposition

157
00:10:52,393 --> 00:10:54,273
and proposed a city construction fee.

158
00:10:54,632 --> 00:10:58,793
In a few days, nearly ten million yuan
in city construction funds was raised.

159
00:10:59,273 --> 00:11:02,712
Afterward, relying on his own prestige,

160
00:11:03,033 --> 00:11:04,752
he adopted a dictatorial approach.

161
00:11:04,913 --> 00:11:08,553
While it fueled Yuehai Town's
rapid economic growth,

162
00:11:08,712 --> 00:11:11,913
it also planted the seeds
of serious risks.

163
00:11:13,153 --> 00:11:15,352
Another leader in Yuehai Town

164
00:11:16,313 --> 00:11:19,752
